race.comment: BUTLER'S CABIN (7) is generally an honest type in the frame at 10 of 21 starts but missed the placings last time when fourth (22.98) over 400m at this track. Drawn out but with clear running expected to go close. MIDNIGHT MASS (2) turned spotting a big start finishing sixth (23.05) last time in a Grade 4/5 at this track. Form here sound including six wins. Consistent performer from this draw with a win and five minor placings to his credit. Will give the top chances plenty to think about. SUNSET OYSTER (3) produced a moderate run last time when sixth at this track over 400m behind Aussie Gem (23.36) in a Grade 4. Worth another chance. SUNSET SAPPHIRE (8) missed the placings here most recently but can sneak into the finish with the right run.
